description: Ash Ketchum and Goh went to the Galar region in order to research Falinks. There they found a group of Falinks that were completely out of sync. It turns out the Falinks accidentally got separated, so Goh goes to help the Brass, the leader, while Ash helps the other Troopers. The Brass was depressed because of its inability to command the troopers. Goh helped it and after a battle with Eiscue, the Falinks wanted to be caught by Goh, which he obliged.
name: Taireetsu (Gou)
